The paper focuses on multimedia delivery through an integrated network, including both a cellular and a broadcast last mile operating over shared spectrum. This suggests that the paper could belong to the Networking and Internet Architecture (cs.NI) category. Additionally, the paper discusses caching and joint processing algorithms, which are topics that fall under the Multimedia (cs.MM) and Information Theory (cs.IT) categories. The paper also mentions an integrated network controller, which could be related to Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing (cs.DC) or Systems and Control (cs.SY) categories. Therefore, the most likely categories are cs.NI, cs.MM, cs.IT, cs.DC, and cs.SY.
